Outbreak;;56;;59;;R;;A dangerous airborne virus threatens civilization in this tense thriller. After an African monkey carrying a lethal virus is smuggled into the U.S., an outbreak occurs in a California town. To control the spread of the disease, a team of doctors is brought in that includes a contagious disease expert (Dustin Hoffman) and his ex-wife (Rene Russo). Once the Army intervenes to handle the situation, though, the doctors must fight against the clock to save the town and its residents.;;Drama,Action,Horror,Mystery & thriller;;Wolfgang Petersen;;1995;;Dustin Hoffman,Rene Russo,Morgan Freeman,Kevin Spacey,Cuba Gooding Jr.,Donald Sutherland,Patrick Dempsey,Zakes Mokae,Malick Bowens,Susan Lee Hoffman,Benito Martinez,Leland Hayward III,Dale Dye;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/outbreak